00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:06.310
So often they'll either have a computer,
or you need to get them a computer

61
00:03:06.310 --> 00:03:09.890
associated with the activity of
what they're going to be doing.

62
00:03:09.890 --> 00:03:13.220
Let them know what software is
available for them to install,

