00:04:11.530 --> 00:04:14.330
And so it's important that you get
them set up and running on whatever

85
00:04:14.330 --> 00:04:18.610
the communication channel is, the one that
your organization particularly focuses on.

86
00:04:20.030 --> 00:04:23.770
And so, after you've got their equipment
set up and you've got them sort of ready

