work on just right away, that day.

98
00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:00.792
They can already start asking questions,

99
00:05:00.792 --> 00:05:02.888
and they can already start
interacting with people.

100
00:05:02.888 --> 00:05:06.846
Ideally, it's a short duration project,
